Class TGMapFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.activities.TGBaseFragment
        • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.fragments.map.base.TGBaseMapFragment
          • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.fragments.map.implementation.TGMapFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.arch.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, TGMapContract.View, TGMapHolder

    public class TGMapFragment
extends TGBaseMapFragment
implements TGMapContract.View
    An implementation of TGBaseMapFragment that allows for search and routing functionality. This class works well with TGTurnByTurnFragment to allow easy implementation of search and navigation. See TallyGoActivity for an example of how this can be used to work with TGTurnByTurnFragment
